  "prompt": "Do we have Financial Management in IPCC group 1 in may 2017? Websites show change in syllabus.",
  "response": "Yes, the Financial Management paper was included in the Intermediate (IPC/IPCC) syllabus for the May 2017 examination. However, it's important to note that the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) has undergone syllabus changes periodically. After the introduction of the new syllabus under the CA Intermediate course in 2016, Financial Management was incorporated in the new structure, replacing some subjects from the old IPC/IPCC format.\n\nIf you are referring to the specific syllabus for the May 2017 exams, Financial Management was indeed part of the curriculum. For the most accurate and up-to-date information, it's always a good practice to check directly with the official ICAI website or refer to the official announcement regarding syllabus changes.",
